name: Disclosure
summary: Various organizations and companies are emphasizing the significance of disclosure practices. Vestas highlights "Rules of Disclosure," while ING Think anticipates heightened attention on company disclosure due to the approaching European Sustainability Reporting Standards (ESRS). Meanwhile, over 400 firms are embracing the Taskforce on Nature-related Financial Disclosures (TNFD) recommendations for nature disclosure, and the IFRS Foundation assumes responsibility for the Taskforce on Private Markets (TPM) transition plan disclosure resources. In the entertainment industry, Disclosure has announced a Glastonbury set featuring Sam Smith as a special guest, and almost 100 firms have committed to the TNFD disclosure framework. The Securities and Exchange Commission's (SEC) Cyber Disclosure Rules, which are now a year old, have provided valuable lessons. Finally, E3G responds to the IFRS announcement, highlighting the importance of clear and consistent disclosure standards.
